# Crimson Sports Complex - Stack

- **Backend**: ASP.NET Core Web API (net9), controllers in `/controllers`
- **Frontend**: Static HTML/CSS/JS in `/wwwroot`, multi-page SPA
- **Design**: Alabama crimson (#9C1B2E) primary, Barlow font, dark charcoal bg
- **Auth**: Client-side session (sessionStorage) - no API auth
- **Pages**: login, dashboard, manager, athlete, reports
